Class SafeDepositReceipt

All Implemented Interfaces:
Message, Publishable
public class SafeDepositReceipt
extends SignedResponse

A signed response from a safe deposit message.

Note that a recipient will use the identifying information in the response to re-contact the "bank" (handling node) for status or withdrawal.

NOTE: The receipt is responsible for interacting with the SafeDepositBox.

Author:
Spence Koehler

Recipient should check the withdrawal for status. If null, the claimTicket should be resubmitted later to retrieve the contents.
